snippet.title: The Smiths
snippet.description: I’m Granger Smith. I’m a husband, father and country music singer. My brothers and I own an apparel company, an American lifestyle brand called YEE YEE. I’m Amber Smith. I’m a wife, a mother, actor and city girl turned country. Together we live on a farm with a lot of animals outside of Austin, Texas. We have four young children. Three of them are here on earth with us and we have one in heaven. We created this show to try to spread honesty and positivity the best way we know how and to keep us accountable in doing so. We share a lot of laughs, a lot of joy but we’re also not afraid to show our heartache and tears. Life is a journey and sometimes it’s all smooth sailing, but sometimes it’s scattered and broken. We’re very grateful for every step of ours, and we hope you’ll join us. Welcome to the Smiths! New 'Smith's' episodes launch every Tuesday and Thursday at 6pm CST! New 'Arise With Amber' episodes launch every Sunday at 8am CST!
